{"tid":303434,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"習近平加薪六成 月薪11385元","createTime":"2017-06-30T07:46:34.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-01T08:43:28.000Z","uid":31208,"like":8,"dislike":116,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"21e04b1a04a2dda29d4f618abca51a1303d19004","tid":303434,"uid":31208,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:46:34.000Z","msg":"【本報訊】內地官方首次披露，公務員體系中最高的正國級官員，最高基本工資已從每月7,020元增加62%至11,385元（人民幣．下同）。一般相信，這就是國家主席習近平的基本薪金。<br />\n<br />\n料為最低工資國家元首<br />\n<br />\n《人民日報》去年11月曾引述中央黨群機關公務員陶磊宣稱，根據公務員工資級別體系，國家主席的工資估計約1萬多元。但官方從未公布最高級公務員的具體水平。<br />\n<br />\n報道引述人力資源和社會保障部公布的信息，正國級官員最高基本工資是年薪是136,620元（折算22,000多美元），即平均每月11,385元（約1,833美元），仍可能是世界主要國家的元首中工資最低。"},{"pid":"e371613a8418d81fb547aa5a2d9cb246881fbd95","tid":303434,"uid":4155,"like":140,"dislike":1,"score":139,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:48:22.000Z","msg":"有其他收入來源又話俾地班人知咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f426fa6d596a57ea600733c9a6419a78280b2920","tid":303434,"uid":90,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:50:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a83cda158c9f97b60376ec9b6f0d16d1379887d","tid":303434,"uid":77196,"like":193,"dislike":1,"score":192,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:50:12.000Z","msg":"香港特首月薪比習近平高N倍成何體統 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e254fd56fdf3ed8f359fa367e7a2d265d9dcb97e","tid":303434,"uid":60545,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-30T07:50:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32434f7200a2988515c81bd35776710766c135e8","tid":303434,"uid":511,"like":20,"dislike":7,"score"